          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross section, energy and angular distributions of",
                "photoprotons from the Li-7(g,p) He-6 reaction are",
                "measured. Three peaks at proton energies 2.3, 3.2 and",
                "3.9 MeV are observed in the energy spectrum. Excited",
                "Li-7 nuclear states with energies 12.5,13.5 and 14.3",
                "MeV respectively, correspond to the three peaks. The",
                "cross sections for the indicated proton groups are",
                "obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
